results.deck: Headstrong Games is a UK-based development house that was formerly known as Kuju London.
results.description: Kuju London was renamed Headstrong Games on July 29, 2008 as the "final piece of the puzzle" for Kuju Entertainment. On August 19 2008, SEGA announced that Headstrong Games would be working on the Wii title House of the Dead: Overkill, thus continuing the Studio's focus on developing for the Nintendo platform.
